Then the authorization module evaluates policies.

Most clusters use RBAC as the authorization mechanism.

Important:

Authorization does NOT modify your request.
It only returns:

Allow 
or
Deny 

If denied â†’ request stops immediately.
If allowed â†’ it moves to Admission Controllers.

So the control plane flow is:

Authentication â†’ Authorization â†’ Admission â†’ etcd

